				<div type="translation">
					<p><!--EHRI-DR-19410719-IT_EN</p>
      <p/>
      <p>Report of the envoy in Bucharest, Renato Bova Scoppa, to the Ministry of Foreign Affairs on
        <date when="1941-08-21">19.7.1941</date>. The report was forwarded to the General Directorates of Demography and Race and
        Public Security on 18 August by Division AG IV.</p>
      <p/>
      <p>R. Legation of Italy, Bucharest</p>
      <p>Cable No. 3314/1371</p>
      <p>Classified--></p>
					<pb facs="EHRI-DR-19410719-IT_01.jpg" n="1"/>
					<p>Addressed to R. <orgName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_cb-005042">Ministry of Foreign Affairs</orgName>, <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/3169070/rome.html">Rome</placeName>.</p>
					<p>Bucharest, <date when="1941-07-19">19th July 1941</date>/XIX</p>
					<p>Re: <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-815" type="subject">Jewish problem</term> in <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/798549/romania.html">Romania</placeName></p>
					<p>The reconquest of <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/571096/bukovina.html">Bukovina</placeName> and of <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/618569/bessarabia.html">Bessarabia</placeName>, where <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-872"
							type="subject">Jewish communities</term> are particularly numerous, has prompted the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-948" type="subject">Government</term> to adopt draconian <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-337"
							type="subject">anti-Jewish measures</term>.</p>
					<p>The <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jewish</term>-<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-1000" type="subject">Communist</term> uprisings in <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/677697/galati.html"
							>Galatz</placeName> and in <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/675810/iasi.html">Jassy</placeName> last month (my telegrams no. 699 and 704 of 29th and 30th June last and no. 707 of 1st inst. ) had already resulted in savage <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-601" type="subject">repressions</term> of a markedly <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-337" type="subject">anti-Semitic</term> nature.</p>
					<p>Now, although it has not been officially declared, the problem of <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-349" type="subject">cleansing</term> the eastern <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/798549/romania.html">Romanian</placeName> territories of
							<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term> is being tackled resolutely and the Authorities in charge strive to solve it as thoroughly as possible and do not hesitate to employ even the most drastic <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/terezin-terms-keyword-jmp-542" type="subject">means</term>. Reportedly <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-518" type="subject">deportations</term>, expulsions and even <term
							ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-541" type="subject">executions</term> are fairly large in numbers. Since news of this had already begun to leak out in the other regions of <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/798549/romania.html"
							>Romania</placeName> as well, it has been considered advisable today to make the following official announcement which attempts to give a plausible reason for events that are actually quite different.</p>
					<p><q>Having ascertained that the <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term> of <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/562153/galicia.html">Galicia</placeName> are trying by all available means to enter <placeName
								ref="http://www.geonames.org/798549/romania.html">Romania</placeName>
							<term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/terezin-terms-keyword-jmp-200" type="subject">illegally</term>, General <persName ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/authorities/ehri_pers-000010">Antonescu</persName> has ordered that the entry of these <term
								ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">elements</term> into <placeName ref="http://www.geonames.org/798549/romania.html">Romanian</placeName> territory be absolutely forbidden. <term
								ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/ehri_terms-864" type="subject">Jews</term> who have crossed the border or who will attempt to do so will be considered <pb facs="EHRI-DR-19410719-IT_02.jpg" n="2"/> as spies and shot. Border guards who allow or are not
							sufficiently alert to prevent this <term ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/terezin-terms-keyword-jmp-200" type="subject">immigration</term> from happening will be punished as accomplices and shot like the guilty <term
								ref="https://portal.ehri-project.eu/keywords/terezin-terms-keyword-jmp-200" type="subject">immigrants</term>.</q></p>
					<p><persName ref="#ehri_dr_scoppa_bova">R. Bova Scoppa</persName></p>
